Đáp án: She is able to pass the exam easily.

Câu 172. We are able to understand the lesson clearly. Gợi ý: We can...
Đáp án: We can understand the lesson clearly.

Câu 173. on the weekends / play badminton / with my dad / I / often /. //
Đáp án: I often play badminton with my dad on the weekends.

Câu 174. do to / What / we / protect the environment / should / ? //
Đáp án: What should we do to protect the environment?

Câu 175. a movie / I am / at / watching / 4 p.m. / . //
Đáp án: I am watching a movie at 4 p.m.

Câu 176. a lot of car chases / often have / and fighting / Action movies / . //
Đáp án: Action movies often have a lot of car chases and fighting.

Câu 177. was / Quang Trung / When / born / ? //
Đáp án: When was Quang Trung born?

Câu 178. don't like / horror movies / I / it's scary / because / . //
Đáp án: I don't like horror movies because it's scary.

Câu 179. the park / Pick up / in / trash / . //
Đáp án: Pick up trash in the park.

Câu 180. noise / Don't / class / make / in / . //
Đáp án: Don't make noise in class.
